ComicInfo.Summary:
Farewell to a Fading Star: A famous movie actress can't accept that she is getting older.
The Brain Thief: After having his mind-reading show exposed as a fraud, The Great Dante gains the ability to actually read minds.
Beyond the Shadows: Vincent has a recurring nightmare that his wife is in danger.
The Menace of the Maze: Two explorers are trapped in a maze of ancient Egyptian pharaoh King Thutmose.
The Deadly Widow's Web!: Gustave Rausch takes advantage of a kindly old woman, but a spider makes sure he gets what he deserves.
